Before 7 years, I was just got astonished while seen one Keralite guy performing on the coke studio floor. But ow I am really proud of Harish, because he once again proved that the hard work will always conquer the Everest one day. Still, this video doesn't get that much recognition as it deserves. Like all other works from Agam, this one has its own signature.


Thanks, Harish for your overwhelming effort to make us joyous with your own pure music!!!
